Appointment,Plus,is,an,online,reservation,software,provider,Business,can,embed,Appointment,Plus,links,onto,their,websites,or,use,Appointment,Plus,as,a,standalone,booking,service,as,their,website,It,also,provides,POS,functions,for,businesses,to,accept,payment,through,the,appointment,making,interface,Their,RESTful,API,provides,functionality,for,integrating,scheduling,making,software,and,replies,in,JSON,and,XML,formats,Developers,must,request,access,to,the,API,and,its,documentation